Summary: I didn't see it when I phototographed the moon only when I opened the file.
divs: Sighting DetailsThere is not much to explain. I am a designer and stepped outside my to take a digital picture of the full moon. I didn't see the image of the UFO when I took the picture, I was focused on the moon. I pulled up the picture of the moon and as I was trying to determine size and crop, I saw the image of the UFO only then. I didn't notice the UFO at all so I have no information of flight, movement, sound, etc. The pictures below have not been manipulated at all, just cropped and arrow inserted to see where to look. The first image is the raw imaged as photographed.
